    "bio": "Whether you're launching your first product or scaling, I'll help you build an AI-powered, data-driven system that runs your business while you focus on strategic growth.\n\nLet's discuss how strategic optimization combined with business intelligence and custom AI agents can transform your operations and accelerate your success.\n\nReady to scale smarter with AI and data?\n\nLet's talk.",
